l%2Fstatus%2F1356633480776531968%3Fs%3D21&h=f22305fc\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/intel/status/1356633480776531968?s=21</a>"},{"pid":"c1c732cce8f34de1d4895f8673101752be2dcb4f","tid":2406502,"uid":28114,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-13T08:54:30.000Z","msg":"自從 Apple 宣佈在 Mac 產品轉用自家晶片後，與 Intel 的關係就急轉直下，最近更推出一系列廣告，針對 Mac 的弱點逐一細數。<br />\n<br />\nIntel 最近在 Twitter 推出一系列的廣告，主要是描述 Mac 的主要弱點，例如遊戲選擇比 PC 少，或者沒有觸控式螢幕等等，這些廣告都連接到 YouTuber Jon Rettinger 的影片上，詳細示範 PC 比 Mac 好的原因。<br />\n<br />\n不過雖然 Intel 近來努力宣傳 PC 比 Mac 優勝的地方，但網民卻並不領情，紛紛表示與其用與處理器性能無關的範疇與 Mac 比較，不如與同樣是 x86 架構的 AMD 比較更加公平。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.macrumors.com/2021/02/11/intel-anti-mac-ad-campaign/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.macrumors.com%2F2021%2F02%2F11%2Fintel-anti-mac-ad-campaign%2F&d=kdQtjCisvz5VKkzPdH2zQ4429F%2FWQzM9xP7K%2BddLk1E%3D&h=a1ab8a65\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.macrumors.com/2021/02/11/intel-anti-mac-ad-campaign/</a>"},{"pid":"24b15030b58b9c6991fd882575c92ea154bdccc6","tid":2406502,"uid":31215,"like":7,"dislike":6,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-13T08:58:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我領情<br />\n講得幾好"},{"pid":"7e8784ce440d72049c45295d36286b2fabebf51c","tid":2406502,"uid":19967,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-13T09:00:04.000Z","msg":"人哋都就出新一代<br />\n而家先嚟攻擊<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cee001383612cd94c0fa5771c8c21fe81a8ac348","tid":2406502,"uid":28114,"like":23,"dislike":1,"score":22,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-13T09:01:18.000Z","msg":"Intel：繼續萬年14nm<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"faceeccbe65884603511c5fa2a28e59d0527a17b","tid":2406502,"uid":27664,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2